    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and would best suit a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. The engine runs very roughly and likely requires a full overhaul, and the transmission struggles to engage properly. Visually, the body has several significant dents, some rust spots starting to form on the wheel wells, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. It is being sold strictly as-is, and I recommend towing it from the lot rather than attempting to drive it home.",
      "price": 4800.0,
